Package model

Class Graph2D

java.lang.Object
model.Graph2D
Direct Known Subclasses:
ChargeGraph2D
public class Graph2D extends Object
The Graph class is used to store and manage a list of IGraphElements. Responsibilities of the Graph class include adding and removing elements as well as knowing its own width and height dimensions.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Charlie Herbert

    • getElements

      public List<IGraphElement> getElements()
      Gets a list of the elements contained by this graph. Note that the elements are not copies, only the list itself. This prevents unexpected adding/removing of elements but still allows element manipulation.
      Returns:
      A list of the elements managed by this graph.
